tellraw @a {"text": "You there...", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Wait, I, the Formless Voice, am here.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Here to help guide you along your path.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Tell me, brave one, when you were first pulled from the void between worlds, did you, perchance, hear a voice?", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "That voice belongs to the Ageless One, both my ally and foe.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "We, the Emissaries of Kirion, have haunted this land since before the day of its founding.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "I seek to protect E'Siraph, to protect its people, as I hope you do too.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But the second reaping threatens the extinction of these people.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Few survive onshore, but hundreds float offshore, waiting for the end, an end that may never come.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "The second reaping began deep below, in a place of riches and fire.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But the reaping's origins matter not.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "It was always coming, and it will come again.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "No matter where you live, disaster strikes eventually.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "In these times, we must try to save as many lives as can be done.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "In this way, the Last King of Tyre speaks the truth.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Do as he says, reactivate all five resonating crystals, purge the land and allow your world a time of peace.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Is this what you already believed?", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "My guidance, hardly as you may think, is worth much.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Soon, you will be tempted.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Stay strong, and do not waver in your path, for nothing matters more than life.", "color": "gray", "italic": true}